akka.actor.testkit.typed.javadsl

Class BehaviorTestKit<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.actor.testkit.typed.javadsl.BehaviorTestKit<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BehaviorTestKitImpl

    public abstract class BehaviorTestKit<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Used for synchronous testing Behaviors. Stores all effects e.g. Spawning of children, watching and offers access to what effects have taken place.

    Not for user extension or instantiation. See BehaviorTestKit.create factory methods

    For asynchronous testing of Behaviors running see ActorTestKit
